# Commit Message Convention

## Format

```
<type>(<scope>): <subject>
<BLANK LINE>
<body>
<BLANK LINE>
<footer>
```

## Types

| Type     | Description                      |
| -------- | -------------------------------- |
| feat     | New feature                      |
| fix      | Bug fix                          |
| docs     | Documentation changes            |
| style    | Formatting, linting fixes        |
| refactor | Code restructuring               |
| test     | Test additions/modifications     |
| chore    | Build process or tooling changes |

## Examples

```
feat(simulink): add neural network block

Implements a trainable neural network block with configurable layers.
Supports both feedforward and recurrent architectures.

Closes #45
```

```
fix(core): handle empty matrix inputs

Fixes indexing error when empty matrices are passed to calculate().
Added validation and unit tests.

BREAKING CHANGE: Now throws MException instead of warning.
```
